{"id":617798,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/09/【立此存照】网安示范高校山东大学发布不良信/","date":"2019-09-17T10:25:26Z","modified":"2019-09-17T10:25:54Z","title":"【立此存照】“网安示范高校”山东大学官微现“不良信息”","content":"<p>9月17日凌晨，有网友发现山东大学官方微博连续发布不良信息。此后，山东大学官方发布声明称系官微被入侵，已采取措施并向警方报案。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/EEonvKTVUAAzgbF.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-617799\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/EEonvKTVUAAzgbF.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"850\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/EEonvKTVUAAzgbF.jpg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/EEonvKTVUAAzgbF-194x300.jpg 194w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/EEonvKTVUAAzgbF-768x1187.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/EEonvKTVUAAzgbF-662x1024.jpg 662w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/EEonvv7VUAEbaI2.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-617800\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/EEonvv7VUAEbaI2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"321\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/EEonvv7VUAEbaI2.jpg 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/EEonvv7VUAEbaI2-300x175.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/EEonvv7VUAEbaI2-768x449.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/EEonvv7VUAEbaI2-1024x598.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/EEonvv7VUAEbaI2-1080x631.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>目前，无法证实山东大学官方微博所发布的信息是由编辑误发还是黑客入侵发布的，另有网友提供线索：山东大学16日刚被列为“一流网络安全学院建设示范项目高校名单”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/EEonwXAUUAAjxMX.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-617801\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/EEonwXAUUAAjxMX.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"579\" 